{"id":32768,"date":"2019-07-12T18:01:13","date_gmt":"2019-07-12T14:01:13","guid":{"rendered":"https:\/\/abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/?p=32768"},"modified":"2023-03-10T10:27:46","modified_gmt":"2023-03-10T06:27:46","slug":"islam-vanishes-end-of-time","status":"publish","type":"post","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2019\/07\/12\/islam-vanishes-end-of-time\/","title":{"rendered":"Hadith on Islam: Disappearance of religious knowledge at end of time"},"content":{"rendered":"<p>Hudhayfah ibn al-Yaman reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201c<strong>Islam will be taken apart just as a garment is taken apart, until fasting is not known, nor prayer, nor rites, nor charity. The Book of Allah Almighty will vanish in a single night, such that no verse of it is left on earth. There will only remain some sects among the people, old men and women who say: We heard our forefathers used to say &#8216;there is no God but Allah,&#8217; so we say it as well.<\/strong>\u201d<\/p>\n<p>Source: Sunan Ibn Ma\u0304jah 4049<\/p>\n<p>Grade: <strong><em>Sahih<\/em><\/strong> (authentic) according to Al-Albani<\/p>\n<p style=\"text-align: right;\">\u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062d\u064f\u0630\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0641\u064e\u0629\u064e \u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0627\u0644\u0652\u064a\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627\u0646\u0650 \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u0631\u064f\u0633\u064f \u0627\u0644\u0652\u0625\u0650\u0633\u0652\u0644\u064e\u0627\u0645\u064f \u0643\u064e\u0645\u064e\u0627 \u064a\u064e\u062f\u0652\u0631\u064f\u0633\u064f \u0648\u064e\u0634\u0652\u064a\u064f \u0627\u0644\u062b\u0651\u064e\u0648\u0652\u06